    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_1780-2171",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1780-2171",
      "markText": "纨裤之子，以赭衣视笠蓑；经生之家，以农夫为诟詈。晨炊晚饷，知其味而忘其源者众矣！",
      "totalCount": 750,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1780&rangeEnd=2171",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1780&rangeEnd=2171"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_3_5572-5677",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5572-5677",
      "markText": "丐大业文人弃掷案头！此书于功名进取毫不相关也",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5572&rangeEnd=5677",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5572&rangeEnd=5677"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_2253-2326",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2253-2326",
      "markText": "不学无术的富家子弟像看待罪犯一样看待农民，饱读诗书的儒生也把农民当作辱骂别人的代称。他们整日饱食，评判美味，却不知道饭食的来处。这种人实在太多了！",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2253&rangeEnd=2326",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2253&rangeEnd=2326"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_3_5100-5128",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5100-5128",
      "markText": "《观象》《乐律》二卷，其道太精，自揣非吾事，故临梓删去。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5100&rangeEnd=5128",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5100&rangeEnd=5128"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_8748-8777",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8748-8777",
      "markText": "黄豆便宜的时候，把黄豆撒在稻田里，一粒黄豆就可以使三寸见方",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8748&rangeEnd=8777",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8748&rangeEnd=8777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_3_6113-6161",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6113-6161",
      "markText": "请那些爱钻研习读儒家经典的文人把它弃置在案头之上吧！这本书于仕途进取是毫无关联、没有丝毫用处的。",
      "totalCount": 196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6113&rangeEnd=6161",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6113&rangeEnd=6161"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_3_3976-4189",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3976-4189",
      "markText": "伤哉贫也！欲购奇考证，而乏洛下之资",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3976&rangeEnd=4189",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3976&rangeEnd=4189"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_7384-7602",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7384-7602",
      "markText": "香稻一种，取其芳气，以供贵人，收实甚少，滋益全无，不足尚也。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7384&rangeEnd=7602",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7384&rangeEnd=7602"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_3_2634-3005",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2634-3005",
      "markText": "幸生圣明极盛之世，滇南车马纵贯辽阳，岭徼宦商衡游蓟北，为方万里中，何事何物不可见见闻闻？",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2634&rangeEnd=3005",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2634&rangeEnd=3005"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_854-1093",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "854-1093",
      "markText": "生人不能久生，而五谷生之；五谷不能自生，而生人生之。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=854&rangeEnd=1093",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=854&rangeEnd=1093"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_3279-3354",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3279-3354",
      "markText": "谷物一直以来没有固定不变的名称。所谓百谷，是从谷物的整体来说的。通常说的五谷，指的是麻、菽、麦、稷、黍这五样，唯独少了水稻，这是因为著书的人是西北人。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3279&rangeEnd=3354",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3279&rangeEnd=3354"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_10_10512-10551",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "10512-10551",
      "markText": "如果用人的小便滋润一下，味道会甘甜、气味会芬芳，这就是所谓的“化臭腐为神奇”。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10512&rangeEnd=10551",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10512&rangeEnd=10551"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_3_375-646",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "375-646",
      "markText": "天覆地载，物数号万，而事亦因之，曲成而不遗。岂人力也哉？",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=375&rangeEnd=646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=375&rangeEnd=646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_3_2480-2512",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2480-2512",
      "markText": "世界上有聪明好学的人，备受尊敬，然而他们连枣花、梨花都分辨不清，",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2480&rangeEnd=2512",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2480&rangeEnd=2512"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_14034-14059",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14034-14059",
      "markText": "所有的病根都在谷种内部，可有人却因此埋怨鬼神作怪。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14034&rangeEnd=14059",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8232ec0813ab7a2dg012c49?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14034&rangeEnd=14059"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050372_4_2723-2753",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2723-2753",
      "markText": "五谷，则麻、菽、麦、稷、黍，独遗稻者，以著书圣贤起自西北也。",
